in Camp by 8 oclock we could all go down in a body so all the men were lined up the old R.S.M. addressed them told them the case all swore they would be back on time. I'll never forget the way the Tommies opened their eyes when they saw heard of this happening, it was a wonderful unheard thing to them They telephoned down to the authorities in Rouen that we were coming were not to be molested for "passes" by the "red caps" or others